jalin n-chi t-xupin t-xu´k). N-ximane qa at nim n-suerte wi´je tu´n n-el oq twitz nya b´a´n n-ok nq´o´ne kyxol xjal ikyjo — a Ministro
axix tok mya b´a´n tu´n tten mas t-xtalb´il wi´je — extzen n-ximane, Ron,
qa mlay txi tqʼoʼna ambʼil kye toj tjaya tuʼn miʼn tok tkeʼyina aju nya bʼaʼn bʼe
t-xilen ky-okslab´il ex ky-b´inchb´en q-tatey. N-chi ayone tu´n tkyaqil wanmiye
