q´uqli jun bruja tuk´e jun t-xaq, q´eq t-xaq n-ku tz´aq tzmax t-q´ob´. Noq b´a´n tu´n ky-b´inchen
qʼonka twitza tiʼj t-xe ttziʼ tuʼnju tzaj tqʼoʼn velo tuʼn tetz chʼin.
