kawb´il toj jaxnaq´tzb´il. Mya aqo´ye t-xe t-xe´chil; Xi nqanine te ajxnaq´tzal
Flitwick qa aye xnaq´tzanjtz tzaj q´o´n amb´il kye tun ky-pon toj Hog's Head,
extzen tzaj tq´ama´n qa b´a´n, noqtzun ayetzi´n tzaj tq´ama´n weye tun t-xi q-i´ne q-lente.
extzen ma tz´ok nq´o´ne nwitze ti´j tkyaqil ti´chaq n-ximane kyi´j k´lojin te xnaq´tzb´il ex
k´lojin aq´untl toj ja extzen b´a´n t-xi q´o´n amb´il kye. noq mya n-ximane qa
jun tb´anel nab´il qa ma tz´ok q-yek´un aju n-b´inchen qu´n.
