A Harry exttzen a George n-chi b´et ky-etz toj b´e, kykab´il n-chi ẍch´in, extzen mya n-chi kyq´ama´n jun yol kyxolx. Aju tqʼajqʼajel ex aju tzeʼn kye xjal chʼiy
