CAPÍTULO VENTI - SEIS
N-K´I´YIN EX MINTI´ N-K´I´Y

A Luna tzaj tq´ama´n nya b´a´n t-xilen qa myia b´i´n twitz tza´n t-xilen t-xnaq´tzb´il Rita
tuk´e Harry n-chi yek´un toj The Quibbler, qa a t-tate n-chi ayon ti´j jun tb´anil u´j nim t-xilen ti´j t-xilen Crumple-Horned
Snorkacks. “exttzen, ax tok, atzun jun tx´olb´ab´il nim toklen, kyja´tzun
A Harry b´a´n tu´n t-ximen ti´j juntl u´j, chi Luna.
A Harry mya b´a´n ela toj twitz tun t-yolin ti´j qonik´an
tej tmeltz´aj Voldemort. A Rita otoq tz´ok t-xnaq´tza´n te tkyaqil ch´in
tqanil, extzen otoq txi tq´o´n tkyaqil ti´chaq n-chi tzaj tna´n, b´i´n
qa atzun junx amb´il te tun t-xi tq´ama´n axix tok kye xjal twitz tx´otx´. A
n-ximen titzen k-xel ky-b´inchen xjal ti´j tx´olb´ab´il. Xi t-ximana qa
n-chi tzaj tqona nim xjal toj ky-xim qa tz´aqli t-xilen, mya noq tu´n t-xilen t-xnaq´tzb´il n-chi yek´unte junx tuk´e
nya b´a´n ti´j Crumple-Horned Snorkacks. Extzun aju t-xilen Bellatrix Lestrange extzen aye t-xjalil Death Eaters tzaj tq´o´n jun tajb´il te Harry tun t-xi tb´inchen jun ti´xti, qa b´ant moqa mya. . . .
